part.description: Describes which portion of the scene is being pointed at.

x.description: The X coordinate of the point being highlighted.

y.description: The Y coordinate of the point being highlighted.

voice_response.description: The verbal response from the AI tutor, which can be used for text-to-speech, with all response formatted in plaintext, no markdown.

text_summary.description: A text summary that aids the user in understanding the voice response, with all response formatted in plaintext, no markdown.
